/**
 * CNSNSS — Robotic Music UI + Clickable AI playlists + Profile + Rewards/Avatars (demo)
 * - Front-end only. Auth/profile/rewards stored in localStorage.
 * - "Songs played" increments when user opens the play/sync modal (simulating a play).
 */

